<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> P. Anastase Marie, in Mash.,vi ٥٢٩ - ٣٦<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> K. Vollers, Volkssprache ١٩٠٦<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> H. Kofler, Reste altarab. Dalekte, WZKM, ١٩٤٠,٦١ - ١٣٠, ٢٣٣ - ٦٢, ١٩٤١,٥٢ - ٨٨, ٢٤٧ - ٧٤; ١٩٤٢, ١٥ - ٣٠, ٢٣٤ - ٥٦<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
